Package: changeofevidence
Type: Package
Title: Change of Evidence
Version: 1.4.2
Author: Moritz Dechamps
Maintainer: Moritz Dechamps <moritz.dechamps@psy.lmu.de>
Description: This package provides functions to test for a change of Bayesian evidence over time which can be used to examine volatile effects. It includes sequential Bayesian testing methods for t-Tests, Non-Parametric Tests, Binomial Tests, and Correlation Tests.
Imports:
    BayesFactor,
    ggplot2,
    patchwork,
    pracma,
    parallel,
    pbapply,
    hypergeo,
    logspline
